post_text:
Join the Roxana Community School District in making a difference. We're raising money to renovate our old weight room and transform it into the Jeff Welker Wellness Center for students, staff and community members. Any donation will help make an impact. Thanks in advance for your contribution to this endeavor and for keeping Jeff Welker's legacy alive. Please help us by donating via cash or check to the Roxana Shells Foundation, or by donating to our GoFundMe page linked below.

post_text:
Coach Welker was a transformational influence in the lives of students, staff, and families in our community. This fundraising campaign provides an opportunity to be a part of a lasting tribute to someone whose life exemplifies what it means to be a Shell.

- History teacher for over 37 years
- Silver Medallion Teacher of the Year, IL
- State Historical Society
- Teacher of the Year
- Emerson Electric Excellence in Teaching
- Civil War re-enactor for 18 years
- Football Coach
- Girls Basketball Coach
- Weight Lifting Coach

post_text:
Any donations made help us reach our goal of making Coach Welker's dream a reality. Please help us by donating via cash or check to the Roxana Shells Foundation, or by donating to our GoFundMe page linked below.

For those who donate at certain amounts, we have some items of recognition:

Gold - $20,000+

- "Pillars of the Project" - Recognition on one of the structural pillars in the wellness center
- Name on the prominently located Wall of Giving
- Invitation to participate in the ribbon cutting ceremony and reception
- Recognition in the sports media guide

Silver - $1000+

- Name on the prominently located Wall of Giving
- Invitation to participate in the ribbon cutting ceremony and reception
- Recognition in the sports media guide

Bronze - $100+

- Invitation to participate in the ribbon cutting ceremony and reception
- Recognition in the sports media guide
